This for tutorial for learning multi threaded application under c++
I have used visual and non visual system from http://www.cs.mtu.edu/~shene/NSF-3/BETA/index.html

I have also used program from http://www.cs.mtu.edu/~shene/NSF-3/e-Book/index.html
I have modified the make file changed the structure for linux. 
I was not able to build the program for windows based system.


To build on ubuntu 14.04, you may require to download packages for gtk1.2 and install it.

Note that, you won't be able to compile it unless you download libraries from above mention website and follow the instructions.



